{"tid":586314,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［誠意道歉］對唔住女朋友   我唔應該咁對你","createTime":"2018-03-09T11:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T12:16:58.000Z","uid":86291,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"67cbdba8e9051f3fffc02748b7cfc1a0e4835005","tid":586314,"uid":86291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:58:32.000Z","msg":"對唔住呀女朋友  我真係無心咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事源是咁樣的   岩岩係我女朋友屋企柯屎開大 <br />\n柯得太急   柯完既時候唔小心柯到成個廁所都係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n包括痴係廁板既一舊中形 堅硬  深啡色屎<br />\n其次仲有係馬桶內壁粒狀既屎 同一啲T字形屎漬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾咁岩起身睇到有屎 知道大獲了 想清潔之際<br />\n仲比女朋友咁岩入到嚟見到全個馬桶都係屎既情況<br />\n雖然我已經馬上即刻用盡所有能力去抹乾淨<br />\n但奈何女朋友有多少潔癖 始終覺得有屎<br />\n仲屌晒鬼 話的咁大個人柯屎都要教 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲話以後唔好掂佢同佢仲聞到成間屋都係屎味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係呢度向我女朋友致最誠懇 最深切既道歉<br />\n我絕對唔係有心整屎落去廁所<br />\n希望你可以原諒我 唔好唔要我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13172bd101f44d60a79334a1584a3484aedfca5","tid":586314,"uid":74380,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:59:51.000Z","msg":"你當呢度fb?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41203e2ed0151071b60fcd2f27595d7424bcc3b2","tid":586314,"uid":41326,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:00:13.000Z","msg":"查看全部回應<br />\n            即時翻譯"},{"pid":"292ea5ff042f9f10ccaeecd6dd955246cbf92371","tid":586314,"uid":174607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:05:16.0